{"tha-ap357:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap357:0.2":"Saddasannakavagga ","tha-ap357:0.3":"Dandadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap357:1.1":"“Kananam vanamogayha, ","tha-ap357:1.2":"velum chetvanaham tada; ","tha-ap357:1.3":"Alambanam karitvana, ","tha-ap357:1.4":"sanghassa adadam aham. ","tha-ap357:2.1":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap357:2.2":"subbate abhivadiya; ","tha-ap357:2.3":"Alambanampi datvana, ","tha-ap357:2.4":"pakkamim uttaramukho. ","tha-ap357:3.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap357:3.2":"yam dandamadadim tada; ","tha-ap357:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap357:3.4":"dandadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap357:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap357:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap357:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap357:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma dandadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap357:6.1":"Dandadayakattherassapadanam pancamam. "}